    <string name="about_description">Extract partition images in parallel from a full Android A/B (payload.bin) OTA.\nSupports local files and OTA direct links, concurrent multi-partition extraction, resumable network downloads, and SHA-256 verification after extraction.\nUI is a bespoke ColorOS 16 “Flux” design.</string>
